user.canProvide: I'm a founding engineer at an early-stage fintech company building a consumer app. I've mainly focused on iOS engineering, design, and product.
user.intro:
I’m a software engineer and designer based in the Bay Area. I previously went to Cal (’19, go bears) and was an iOS engineer at Twitter. A few years ago, I joined an early-stage startup called Daffy as a founding engineer. We’re building a consumer app that helps people make giving a habit & part of their financial system.

I enjoy getting active & trying new workout classes with friends. I also love traveling to new places (most recently lived in Colombia & Mexico for 2+ months). Super excited to be a part of this community and meet a lot of you soon!
user.lookingFor: Gain skills related to starting a company & entrepreneurship, connect with other product-minded engineers/designers
